Class ProvisioningTarget

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      sailpoint.object.ProvisioningTarget
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
public class ProvisioningTarget
extends AbstractXmlObject

An object that can be stored in a ProvisioningProject that defines the information that must be gathered from the user in order to complete provisioning for this assignment.
